stimulus: Welcome to the experiment. Press any key to begin.

In this experiment, you will be shown short movies containing two objects. One of the objects will be moving toward the other.

In these movies, the moving object either collides with the stationary object, or it comes to a stop before reaching the stationary object. However, you will be shown a clipped version of the movie that does not reveal the ending.

Please watch each clip carefully. Then predict whether or not the two objects will collide later on in the video.

Press the "F" key for yes, the objects will collide.

Press the "J" key for no, the objects will not collide.

Press any key to start.

You can take a quick break now if you need it.

Press the spacebar to continue.
